This paper discusses a new approach to local state trajectory learning for autonomous driving using deep neural networks and genetic algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), as the paper deals with autonomous vehicles. The paper also discusses deep learning solutions, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses perception-planning deep neural networks, which makes cs.CV (Computer Vision) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with motion control, which makes cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible sub-category.
